edu.cnm.deepdive.rps.model

Class Arena.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.rps.model.Arena.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    Arena

    public static class Arena.Builder
extends Object
    Implements the builder pattern to construct instances of Arena. The fluent programming style may be used: each non-terminal method returns the current Builder instance, so multiple invocations may be chained.
